extendedInfo.description: Completely Offline & FREE!! Smallest(Just 200kb!!) dream dictionary app with largest collection of dreams and meanings!!Dreams are progressive images, emotions, moods & sensations that gets processed involuntarily in the mind during certain stages of sleep. Mental states related to dreams such as lucid dreaming, dream recall, dream interpretation and information on meanings of deep nightmares, arenât commonly taught in our schools. Hence here is a dream dictionary handbook containing crisp and clear meanings of dreams.Dream analysis is often tough. This is a dream dictionary app for dream analysis & interpretations. Facts read that dreams are the key to best sleep(sweet dreams) as well as worst sleep (nightmares), and may vary with age. Teenage dreams of girls and boys are different from adult dreams. Interpretations of dreams provided in this dream interpreter app for android phones, can be read totally FREE!! Just search for the dream and understand the meaning of your dreams.If you are a lucid dreamer, its time to take out your dream diary and search meanings for all your dreams in this app.Analysis shows that common dreams are on animals in zoo, weddings, heights, colors, house, books, tv soap casts, dresses and many other aspects of job, marriage and life. This encyclopedia of dreams have meanings for all of the above. Try this meaning analyzer app book today, FREE!Support the developer/finder of these apps with your positive feed back & good ratings, so that we can bring to you more of quality useful apps for FREE on demand! reviews.title: Mediocre
reviews.comment: An average app that has its perks and it\'s pitfalls. There aren\'t that many search terms and the ones that are there don\'t have a very detailed meaning for you to read. Having said this, the app itself doesn\'t take up much phone memory, it can be quickly downloaded and installed and you don\'t need an internet connection once the initial download is complete. Plus, it\'s free so I guess that has to count for something!
